ALTER TABLE bid_adjustment_history 
ADD COLUMN actual_profit_7d DECIMAL(10,2) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '7天实际利润',
ADD COLUMN actual_profit_14d DECIMAL(10,2) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '14天实际利润',
ADD COLUMN actual_profit_30d DECIMAL(10,2) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '30天实际利润',
ADD COLUMN actual_impressions_7d INT DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '7天实际展现',
ADD COLUMN actual_clicks_7d INT DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '7天实际点击',
ADD COLUMN actual_conversions_7d INT DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '7天实际转化',
ADD COLUMN actual_spend_7d DECIMAL(10,2) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '7天实际花费',
ADD COLUMN actual_revenue_7d DECIMAL(10,2) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '7天实际收入',
ADD COLUMN tracking_updated_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '效果追踪更新时间',
ADD COLUMN rolled_back_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '回滚时间',
ADD COLUMN rolled_back_by VARCHAR(255) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '回滚操作人';
